*Raid Attendance Rules*<br>
All Federation raids will be sign up raids. These raids will be added to the Federation Calendar as soon as possible after planning. On the calendar will be a link to a sign in page. If you wish to attend the raid, sign up is MANDATORY. If you sign up, please make every effort to attend. If you later find you are not able to make the raid, please update this on the sign up page as soon as possible.<br>
<br>
Members arriving late to a raid with out prior approval by raid leader, will not be able to attend that raid. If prior plans with the raid leader are made, it is your responsibility to get to the raid, get to where we are, and let the raid leader know that you are there. Do Not put the raid in jeopardy. <br>
<br>
